{"tid":711440,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界盃】被封「最性感球迷」 俄羅斯金髮索女竟係AV女優","createTime":"2018-06-21T14:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T10:34:17.000Z","uid":14503,"like":167,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"7db0a515160104c20b8396b1ebdb5a5db4a06173","tid":711440,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180621/large/1529539938_6059.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180621%2Flarge%2F1529539938_6059.jpg&h=9f394a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涅米諾娃吸引球迷目光，有網民特地起她的底。(互聯網) <br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯世界盃揭幕戰當天場內出現一位金髮索女，被譽為「最性感女球迷」，網民更開始對她「起底」，發現她背景不簡單。 <br />\n<br />\n那位在莫斯科盧日尼基球場（Luzhniki Stahim）為主隊搖旗吶喊的美女，吸引不少球迷的目光，連俄羅斯官方官方通訊社也有發佈她的相片。 <br />\n<br />\n既是「世盃女神」，網民又怎會放過了解她的機會。有人從照片發現她的世界盃球迷證，用證上名字作「人肉搜尋」，最終發現那位叫涅米諾娃（Natalya Nemchinova）的28歲靚女，是色情片演員，有多齣作品，而且有多個藝名。 <br />\n<br />\n網民又發現涅米諾娃已婚，丈夫大她18歲，是健身中心老闆。 <br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"3a8cee0f10ab71599f156f4fc428d26ecc32d380","tid":711440,"uid":14503,"like":307,"dislike":4,"score":303,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgbox.com/vKj6I0FE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgbox.com%2FvKj6I0FE.jpg&h=67a3e722&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7461a1f718d942e11fa6edb14e538ba7fae95ef3","tid":711440,"uid":14503,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:03:24.000Z","msg":"有冇人搵到seed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15860e015e5b51044f2ffa1661c65b9bb1